The Peter Schiff Show
Wednesday, 19 October 2011


[sebaygo1]


Today's guests are Sen. Rand Paul, junior senator from Kentucky, on his alternative plan to create jobs, 
and 
Karen Kwiatkowski, former Pentagon official and Republican candidate for Virginia's 6th district, on her anonymously penned controversial articles Insider Notes from the Pentagon and her recent foray into politics.
